metadata.name: The Joker
metadata.description:
"Be careful who you call a King...

All the romantic girls want a "knight in shining armor"  
All princesses want some noble prince to sweep them off their feet.

I want the Joker.  
Who can outwit the knight in a fight with only his words,  
Who can make a king laugh with accents and gestures so absurd  
Who can cause the rebel to cry and fly away like a scared little bird.

I want the Joker."

- by William Worthless

(Artwork created with Midjourney - Ai)
